{
  "stem": "945.5",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I certainly am thankful for whatever they did to help us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But then my brother and I stuck out on our own.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We ventured into-- first we found jobs.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We moved to Winnipeg.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We found jobs in Winnipeg.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Then we started in the cattle business.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we struggled on with life.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We were very young.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We had big responsibilities.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We wanted to get our parents out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So not only did we have to care for ourselves, but we had to care for them and for our younger brother, Sam.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And thanks God, we got them out-- via Israel, but we got them out.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And life was very difficult, being without money, and without a trade, and without anybody to really help us, and having to carry that burden.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But we carried on.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We were fighters.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And thanks God, now that I look back, we-- we got married.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "My younger brother finished his schooling.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Unfortunately, while we were in the-- on the farm, we had a terrible accident that my dad, having survived a war and having survived a concentration camp, died in a tractor accident.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "My dad had a very difficult time adjusting.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "He was a broken man, like I said from before.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "He lived in a strange country, strange language, no friends, no acquaintances.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "He couldn't do anything to help.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "He felt he was lost.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "But unfortunately, like I said, there was a terrible tragedy.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "He died.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "So after he died, we left that area and my mother and my younger brother lived with us for some time.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "My youngest brother Sam was a very determined man, a young man.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "He wanted to get an education.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Worked hard, got an education, then they moved to Ottawa and my mother went with him.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
